    <item>
      <title>Symphony of Industry</title>
      <link>https://colourlessspearmint.github.io/blog/industry/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://colourlessspearmint.github.io/blog/industry/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://colourlessspearmint.github.io/media/industry.webp&#34; alt=&#34;A complex and massive industrial chamber robotic arms, an assembly line, and welding sparks, all doused in cold blue light; generated with Imagen 3&#34; /&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;blockquote class=&#34;centered-blockquote&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;The dawn&amp;rsquo;s first light, a furnace glow,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Steel muscles flex, the pistons go.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;A rhythmic clang, a hammer&amp;rsquo;s blow,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;The symphony of industry starts to flow.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Clang, clank, bang, the gears engage,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;A chorus of belts on a metal stage.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Whines and hisses, a steamy rage,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;As pistons pump in their measured cage.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
